      "authorityKey": "usgs",
      "retrievedDate": "2026-07-14",
      "quotedText": "GNIS has no dam-specific entry for Keswick Dam; location corroborated via OSM/Nominatim's \"Keswick Dam\" node (40.6117647,-122.4457785), cross-checked against its bounding box (40.6114–40.6122 lat, -122.4474–-122.4441 lon), and anchored to the Sacramento River's GNIS stream record (gaz_id 1654949); correcting the file's prior coordinate (-122.298,41.18), which sat ~64km northeast of the true dam location, within the Dunsmuir/Sweetbriar portion of the regulated reach rather than at the reach's Keswick Dam boundary."
    }
